60
00:05:01,545 --> 00:05:04,807
[SPEAKER_08]: So right now our total population is approximately 60,708.

61
00:05:08,738 --> 00:05:13,302
[SPEAKER_08]: although it increases every year and has been increasing at least since 2010.

62
00:05:13,422 --> 00:05:18,186
[SPEAKER_08]: We're pretty evenly split between male and female.

63
00:05:18,206 --> 00:05:28,635
[SPEAKER_08]: 22.5% is foreign born and approximately one out of three residents speak a language other than English in the home.

64
00:05:29,505 --> 00:05:39,911
[SPEAKER_08]: which is I think something we should keep in mind when we do our outreach and see if we could have other languages potentially available for people that wanna come to any of our sessions.

65
00:05:41,232 --> 00:05:47,756
[SPEAKER_08]: Approximately 5% of people under 65 have a disability, seven or seven to 8% live in poverty, approximately 20% have incomes above 200,000.

66
00:05:56,374 --> 00:06:02,820
[SPEAKER_08]: were pretty evenly split between renters and owner occupied housing.

67
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:12,128
