291
00:27:05,092 --> 00:27:17,103
[SPEAKER_06]: minority populations into a bunch of different wards in a way that kept them from being able to elect people like them, whether that be similar skin color, similar language, similar background, whatever else.

292
00:27:19,284 --> 00:27:24,569
[SPEAKER_06]: And that certainly fully at-large voting is one way of doing that, right?

293
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:31,255
[SPEAKER_06]: Because it means that a minority population will never be a full majority.

