01:11:07,868 --> 01:11:11,451
[SPEAKER_04]: So that might get to that piece a little bit, but I don't wanna, I'm not prepared to say that.

827
01:11:11,471 --> 01:11:13,713
[SPEAKER_04]: I wanna look at some more research and then get back to the committee.

828
01:11:13,953 --> 01:11:19,398
