01:16:58,643 --> 01:17:00,243
[SPEAKER_08]: They go into communities and they

887
01:17:01,758 --> 01:17:04,720
[SPEAKER_08]: ask questions, or they just listen to the community on a topic.

888
01:17:04,820 --> 01:17:09,983
[SPEAKER_08]: So what we came up with is a list of 10 places.

