01:17:54,910 --> 01:18:01,055
[SPEAKER_08]: Milva is hoping we can do these October, November, December, so that we maybe January.

897
01:18:03,137 --> 01:18:05,399
[SPEAKER_08]: We think we should have two people.

898
01:18:05,619 --> 01:18:09,343
[SPEAKER_08]: So one could facilitate the listening session and a note taker.

899
01:18:11,064 --> 01:18:14,207
[SPEAKER_08]: So that we can get the information from the listening session.

900
01:18:15,776 --> 01:18:22,101
